# Hello!
###  And welcome to a collection of projects completed during my time at the Software Guild beginning in February, 2016.
These projects are representative of my very first step(s) into the world of software development by way of Java/JavaScript/MySQL and include console apps, MVC apps, and a CMS website/blog.
